<h1>About Resolve to Save Lives</h1>

<p class="intro">At Resolve to Save Lives we have one mission: save lives. We will save 100 million lives by implementing proven solutions to prevent heart disease and stroke, the world’s leading cause of death. And we are helping the world prevent the next disease outbreak by catalyzing country action to find, stop and prevent new disease threats.</p>

<p>With $225 million dollars from Bloomberg Philanthropies, the Chan Zuckerberg Initiative, and the Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation, Resolve to Save Lives uses proven strategies to take urgent action that improves health in low- and middle-income countries.</p>

